"By all Hawks!!" said Winlord While Trinity woke up, the male looked 
the child while he put her on the floor "Wake up, little-one, I need 
your help"

"How can I help Uncle Windlord, how can I help????"said happyly 
Trinity while she was jumping around the male.

"I need that you help me to care Grounded, just a while" said 
Windlord who had seen and took Grounded "Can you do it??"


"Yup I can Uncle!!1" said the child, who was happy to help.

"COme "said kindly Windlord to Terrataur "conference room is near of 
Crs"

He waited Terrataur's answer
